                    Scene @CONSUME: Pop Puck, dispatch on value.

Hamlet: Recall your past!
Hamlet: Are you as good as a pig?
Hamlet: If so, let us proceed to scene @FINISH.
Hamlet: Are you as good as the sum of a big big big cat and a big cat?
Hamlet: If not, let us proceed to scene @NOT_NL.

                    Scene @MAYBE_BOUNDARY: Puck is newline; check Hamlet for deferred newline.

Hamlet: Am I as good as the sum of a big big big cat and a big cat?
Hamlet: If so, let us proceed to scene @BOUNDARY.
Puck: You are as good as the sum of a big big big cat and a big cat!
Hamlet: Let us return to scene @CONSUME.

                    Scene @NOT_NL: Puck is not newline; flush deferred newline if any, push char.

Hamlet: Am I as good as the sum of a big big big cat and a big cat?
Hamlet: If not, let us proceed to scene @JUST_PUSH.
Puck: Remember yourself!
Puck: You are as good as me!
Puck: Remember yourself!
Hamlet: Let us return to scene @CONSUME.

                    Scene @JUST_PUSH: Push the current char onto Hamlet.

Puck: You are as good as me!
Puck: Remember yourself!
Hamlet: Let us return to scene @CONSUME.

                    Scene @BOUNDARY: Saw two consecutive newlines; push paragraph-close and paragraph-open.

